Package: libtd365-1
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: TD365 Trading API Library (shared library)
 A C++ library for interfacing with the TD365 trading platform API.
 .
 This library provides a modern C++ interface to access TD365 trading platform
 features including authentication via OAuth, real-time WebSocket data
 streaming, and market data access.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: libtd365-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libtd365-1 (= ${binary:Version}),
         ${misc:Depends},
         libboost-all-dev (>= 1.83),
         libssl-dev,
         nlohmann-json3-dev,
         zlib1g-dev,
         libspdlog-dev
Description: TD365 Trading API Library (development files)
 A C++ library for interfacing with the TD365 trading platform API.
 .
 This library provides a modern C++ interface to access TD365 trading platform
 features including authentication via OAuth, real-time WebSocket data
 streaming, and market data access.
 .
 This package contains the development files (headers and static library).
